nodes.text: Lellel was a Hutt with a masculine personality who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War. Lellel was the leader of the Jiramma Hutt clan. The Jiramma clan frequently went into business with the Hutts of the Vanderijar kajidic and Lellel used Jiramma's close ties to the Galactic Empire to help cover up indiscretions that arose due to Vanderijar's aggressive style of operation.
